{"tid":759983,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一日一J","createTime":"2018-07-29T06:43:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T13:09:25.000Z","uid":137521,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fabc8a927bb01e1ed98fa1cf889612816b9933e8","tid":759983,"uid":137521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T06:43:35.000Z","msg":"近排返工壓力好大，成日一放工就想打J發洩，情況持續左成半個月，開始發現自己記性真係差左，無論幾早訓(11點訓)，訓足八個鐘，個人都好似訓唔夠，其他同事都有問做咩好似殘左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到底點先可以返轉頭呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似上左癮咁，日日唔打就周身唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家到底係點戒丁架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"887721661e6daae51c62b3844f4150e2e697c3f7","tid":759983,"uid":42243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T06:44:18.000Z","msg":"一想打J就去照鏡"},{"pid":"eff66720ca5b3745ca516fb240900bc0f1acad1f","tid":759983,"uid":137521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"887721661e6daae51c62b3844f4150e2e697c3f7","tid":759983,"uid":42243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T06:44:18.000Z","msg":"一想打J就去照鏡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T06:44:52.000Z","msg":"有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98126f873053408d04def92205f4869b40535910","tid":759983,"uid":137521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T06:47:42.000Z","msg":"救命呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又想打啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人救下我或者share下心得"},{"pid":"9d7911c6aee92a353538b35490381112d817ea80","tid":759983,"uid":137521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T06:48:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi